1. Log into Lazada
2. Go to campaign page
3. View all campaigns
4. Find which campaigns are “available” tag
    1. From the “available campaign“ tag, 
        loop through them and find the voucher campaign ( cong voucher ) tag
    2. Loop through the voucher Campaign tag
        1. if the dialog appears click “ Lưu “
        2. click the first Promotion and join Now
        3. If meet condition, click “Tham gia ngay“
        4. sign up by fill up in PLACEHOLDER ( follow pic 11)
        5. submit
